description:
Counsel for the Heart - Program 9:  Dating or Courtship - Part 9 of 13. Every-day people have issues, even those we love and live with. Its where the heart is most vulnerable that we suffer from broken relationships and past hurts. And sometimes we experience conflict, rebellion, or disillusionment in our circle of love.

Junie Lawson has worked for over 20 years as a Bible Instructor, one-on-one in homes. She has counseled hundreds of individuals, always using Gods word to bring courage and strength to the heart. In this 13-part series, she shares practical, down-to-earth principles to help make the family strong.
